    "Large language models (LLM) such as ChatGPT and GPT-4 are making significant strides towards the development of Artificial General Intelligence (AGI) (1, 2).",
    "Advanced generative AGI holds the potential to improve patient care (3, 4) and streamline healthcare processes (3, 5).",
